# Festival Chat Environment Variables

# For local development (both app and signaling on localhost)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SIGNALING_SERVER=http://localhost:3001

# For ngrok testing - you'll need to create a separate ngrok tunnel for signaling
# Step 1: Start your app with `npm run dev:all`
# Step 2: Create ngrok tunnel for main app: `ngrok http 3000`
# Step 3: Create ngrok tunnel for signaling: `ngrok http 3001` (in separate terminal)
# Step 4: Set this variable to the signaling tunnel URL:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SIGNALING_SERVER=https://your-signaling-tunnel.ngrok-free.app

# Example:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SIGNALING_SERVER=https://abc123-signaling.ngrok-free.app
